casebody.data:
Flynn, Respondent, v. Manchester, Appellant. (Common Pleas of New York City and County, General Term. February 27, 1891.) Appeal from second district court.

Argued before Bischoff and Pryor, JJ.

Howe & Hummel, for appellant. J. Callahan, for respondent.

No opinion. Judgment reversed, new trial ordered, costs to abide event.
